data.description: NEW LISTING & PRICED RIGHT! Searching for Direct Gulf Access w/easy commute to Downtown Ft Myers & the Beaches? Your Search is Over! Explore this Beautiful Waterfront Pool Home located in SE Cape Coral's Desirable "Everest Neighborhood" just Mins to the River from your Backyard! The Light & Airy Open Concept Boast almost 2000 Sq Ft of Living Space & Features 3 Beds, 2 Baths +Den. Beautifully Updated Interior w/Gorgeous Plank Tile Floors thru-out, Well Appointed Kitchen offers an Abundance of Cabinet & Storage Options, Quartz Countertops, SS Appliances & Huge Island Perfect for Entertaining Guest. Den would make an Excellent Home Gym, Office or Additional Guest Bedroom! Pocketing Sliders open to your Inviting Lanai & Pool Area. There's a Wonderful Patio on the Side Yard offering Privacy & Plenty of Sunshine to work on your Tan! Recent Updates include Newer Roof & AC (2021), Refinished Pool Interior w/New Brick Pavers, Updated Baths w/Tile & Glass Shower, Impact Windows, plus Beautiful Tropical Landscaping. Boaters will enjoy the 2min Ride to River & NO BRIDGES! Horton Park is just down the street, perfect for launching your Boat or Jet Skis. It just doesn't get any better than this!
